/* Early life */   It said that Abdel Al-Mumin was born in the Hammadid Kingdom. This is incorrect, Almohads expanded eastward by 1080 AD all the way to Algiers and conquered Hammadid territories. Tlemcen was under Almoravids rule before Abdel al-Mumin was born. So he was into the land of the Almoravids.orn.

Ada Lovelace isn't the first algorithm programmer simply because in order for Charles to validate his analytical engine he would have written instruction code to test his engine, which he did (difference engine). This by necessity makes him the first computer engineer and programmer.
